Popular actress Opeyemi Aiyeola has debunked rumours that her son is ill. The actress took to her Instagram page to thank her fans for their love and kindness when a post was shared in Facebook stating that her son is seriously ill and need help. “I will like to cease this opportunity to thank most loving n concerned families, friends n fans who have taken it upon themselves to reach out to me with regards a devilish act cursed by an individual/individuals as seen in the attached fb post,” she wrote. She said that her son is alright and her family are healthy. “People, my champs are well, kicking, hale n hearty to Jehovah be the glory,” she said.